Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.32,0:24:34.32,EDTitle,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(315,240)}红莲的思念
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-------------------SUB-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.87,0:01:49.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦突入  便没有退路了是也
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.33,0:01:49.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.39,0:01:51.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.47,0:01:53.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以确定的只有…现在非去不可
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.73,0:01:55.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解是也
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.43,0:01:58.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到时候就会得出答案了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.31,0:02:00.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为一个火雾战士
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.82,0:02:01.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.15,0:02:03.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突入
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.27,0:02:13.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜…保护了我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.99,0:02:16.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过是个密斯提斯的我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.62,0:02:20.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.93,0:02:21.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.33,0:02:24.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定要把悠二给…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.81,0:03:16.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看样子没有布下结界是也
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.29,0:03:21.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  应该非常清楚我们已经突入了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.79,0:03:22.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可大意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.37,0:03:23.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.28,0:03:43.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火雾战士
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.90,0:03:46.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.11,0:03:59.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在星黎殿里应该住着「化装舞会」的红世之徒们的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.06,0:04:01.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太安静了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.57,0:04:03.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连磷子的气息都没
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.31,0:04:16.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是在这里面了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.09,0:04:19.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不断溢出庞大的存在之力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.41,0:04:21.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二就在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.10,0:04:22.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.61,0:04:28.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎并不打算把零时迷子藏起来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.37,0:04:29.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.70,0:04:35.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  已经没有时间来慎重地应付了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.41,0:04:43.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  你就叫夏娜好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.66,0:04:50.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.77,0:04:53.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要我们其中一人先到达零时迷子那里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.62,0:04:55.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就还有宛转余地
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.87,0:04:57.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用理会对方  只管前进
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.79,0:04:58.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.25,0:05:03.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的…你的答案是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.67,0:05:06.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时间紧迫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.49,0:05:38.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对手竟然是那么大的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.35,0:05:40.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平井没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.87,0:05:44.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.82,0:05:46.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.09,0:05:47.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.48,0:05:50.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到处都布满了像自在式一样的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.42,0:06:06.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.21,0:06:09.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妨碍实验的鼠辈们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.33,0:06:12.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多米诺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.68,0:06:16.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  准备完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.25,0:06:21.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妨碍实验的人就用来实验
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.76,0:06:24.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来我「混沌的圣庙」这个题目
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.81,0:06:30.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就拿她们来进行回收再利用啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.26,0:06:47.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像有什么在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.25,0:06:49.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红世之徒？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.61,0:06:51.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.59,0:07:51.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些家伙…是磷子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.44,0:07:53.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机器人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.20,0:07:55.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是「探耽求究」么…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.62,0:07:57.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.40,0:08:23.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才那是什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.01,0:08:25.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,存在之力给吸走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.05,0:08:27.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.09,0:08:31.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大成功！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.92,0:08:37.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把入侵者的力量吸收进温酒瓶内加以利用的自在法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.92,0:08:37.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}温酒瓶：应该是指储存「存在之力」的容器  神经病教授对它的爱称
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.24,0:08:41.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是优秀的作品啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.68,0:08:42.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  教授
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.44,0:08:45.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.85,0:09:16.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「探耽求究」那混蛋  耍这种卑鄙的伎俩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.17,0:09:19.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是让我们轻松进来的理由吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.41,0:09:21.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这些磷子却在动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.44,0:09:26.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕是那家伙做了特别处理吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.10,0:09:27.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了是也
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.60,0:09:38.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贽殿遮那…好重
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.13,0:09:42.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此  所能依靠的只有自身掌握的体术了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.12,0:09:45.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回想起在天道宫时的感觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.81,0:09:46.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.71,0:09:57.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经没有退路了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.66,0:09:58.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.57,0:10:02.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有朝着零时迷子前进
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.09,0:10:08.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多么讽刺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.78,0:10:11.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外面明明充斥着存在之力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.28,0:10:28.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜她…正在战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.30,0:10:30.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战斗…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.33,0:10:33.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,城市里充满了存在之力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.26,0:10:35.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为零时迷子的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.17,0:10:41.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实想要保护城市的话这样是最好的也说不定
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.56,0:10:43.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最好的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.59,0:10:48.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.83,0:10:50.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明只是个单纯的密斯提斯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.19,0:10:52.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.46,0:10:55.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你要进入我里面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.46,0:10:57.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.77,0:11:00.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你正在进入我的里面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.70,0:11:03.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的思念正在填满着我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.05,0:11:07.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我至今为止一直在祈祷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.11,0:11:09.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寻求着答案
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.26,0:11:11.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这肯定就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.87,0:11:16.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…再给我…再把你给我些
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.99,0:11:20.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.39,0:11:49.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.01,0:12:14.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  到底能撑到什么时候呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.21,0:12:16.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要赌一下  「千变」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.75,0:12:19.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你难道忘了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.96,0:12:23.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对手可是那个「天壤劫火」和「梦幻冠带」哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.87,0:12:28.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为容器的火雾战士如果不能使用存在之力的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.33,0:12:31.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不就和普通的人类一样嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.08,0:12:35.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且「混沌的圣庙」已经完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.81,0:12:39.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,存在之力只会永远地增加下去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.09,0:13:45.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是在那里战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.51,0:13:47.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.20,0:13:49.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油啊  平井
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.71,0:13:52.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.00,0:14:21.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好  存在之力开始活性化了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.81,0:14:36.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没完没了是也
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.46,0:14:50.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是在计算之中么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.11,0:14:52.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.80,0:14:55.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为礼炮来说似乎有点夸张了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.81,0:15:04.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,精彩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.22,0:15:10.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这才正是谁也没见过的  注入过盛存在之力的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.39,0:15:16.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教…教授  以后会变什么样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.38,0:15:19.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是因为不知道才要做实验
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.04,0:15:24.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了了解这世界的一切  法则  真理
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.12,0:15:31.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坂井同学  小缘
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.95,0:15:37.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不妙…虽然不知道发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.93,0:15:39.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但总觉得大事不妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.45,0:15:44.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  这城市到底会变成什么样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.39,0:15:53.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  听得到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.91,0:15:55.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,启作  荣太
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.09,0:15:57.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.32,0:15:59.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说听没听到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.03,0:16:03.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,启作  荣太  快回答
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.25,0:16:02.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大…大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.79,0:16:06.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.44,0:16:10.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊哈哈哈  看来还活着呢  两位
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.08,0:16:12.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.96,0:16:15.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就因为那个什么火雾战士的使命的玩意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.43,0:16:16.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还真敢说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.89,0:16:18.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是拼命赶过来的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.29,0:16:21.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别管了  马上去玻璃坛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.97,0:16:22.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有事要调查
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.82,0:16:23.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经在了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.38,0:16:25.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…所以说那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.20,0:16:28.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是说早就在玻璃坛等着啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.94,0:16:30.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要调查什么快给我说出来！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.66,0:16:34.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈哈哈  干得不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.88,0:16:39.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊  刚才的口气就当我没听到好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.02,0:16:41.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看下星黎殿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.48,0:16:42.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星黎殿？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.86,0:16:45.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是浮在空中大得要死的城堡啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.68,0:16:47.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小鬼们好像冲进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.93,0:16:50.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却中了奇怪的自在法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.54,0:16:51.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.24,0:16:55.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,调查一下这个自在式是从城堡的哪里发出的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.01,0:16:56.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.03,0:16:57.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.04,0:17:01.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教育的成果呢  不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.63,0:17:03.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还真是不错的小弟们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.00,0:17:04.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.15,0:17:07.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐藤  回来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.79,0:17:09.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大姐她回来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.73,0:17:11.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.41,0:17:14.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是任性的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.75,0:17:20.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.92,0:17:34.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再来一首动听的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.87,0:17:37.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  再来一首动听的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.49,0:17:40.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你了  好好听着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.45,0:17:44.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿  再来一首动听的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.04,0:17:54.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正中靶心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.02,0:17:59.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,NO
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.46,0:18:01.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.15,0:18:05.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迎…迎击用的自在法发生装置给…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.26,0:18:08.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弄坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.18,0:18:10.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么！？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.60,0:18:24.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「悼词朗诵者」好像回来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.61,0:18:30.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  为什么火雾战士要到处破坏新的尝试呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.12,0:18:32.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果把她们一起吸进去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.13,0:18:34.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赫卡特也会分心的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.32,0:18:36.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去收拾好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.43,0:18:44.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样的话我也不得不动手了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.98,0:18:49.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来被「悼词朗诵者」救了是也
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.86,0:18:50.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.72,0:18:53.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.15,0:18:57.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个气息是…「逆理之裁者」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.60,0:19:08.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎大驾光临
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.27,0:19:10.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是应该说声「好久不见了」？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.80,0:19:13.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是希望你不要碍事就好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.41,0:19:16.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.65,0:19:18.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都做了那么奇怪的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.03,0:19:20.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天可不允许中途退出哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.23,0:19:23.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,周围也充满了存在之力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.84,0:19:25.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼此尽全力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.13,0:19:26.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.55,0:19:30.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在变成冤家之前分个高下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.06,0:19:39.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你先走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.10,0:19:42.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要一个人到就行了是也
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.76,0:19:45.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,答案…应该已经有了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.94,0:19:46.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.90,0:19:49.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于密斯提斯的破坏…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.92,0:19:50.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会破坏的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.03,0:19:55.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意思说要让世界的平衡崩溃么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.92,0:19:57.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也不会让它发生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.43,0:20:00.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威尔艾米娜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.77,0:20:02.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是炎发灼眼的讨伐者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.52,0:20:05.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但还有另一个叫夏娜的我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.50,0:20:07.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使命会完成
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.13,0:20:11.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但却不想把密斯提斯…悠二破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.43,0:20:12.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪一个都是我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.88,0:20:14.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少了哪个都不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.01,0:20:22.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我并不是单纯的火雾战士
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.45,0:20:24.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为炎发灼眼的夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.53,0:20:25.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只进行自己所相信的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.35,0:20:27.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样决定的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.50,0:20:37.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快走是也
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.26,0:20:39.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然你已经决定
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.90,0:20:41.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再说下去也没用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.78,0:20:42.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威尔艾米娜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.48,0:20:44.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我坚信着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.35,0:20:47.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信那是纯粹的你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.90,0:20:50.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.27,0:20:52.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战斗之后再见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.26,0:20:55.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「万条巧手」「梦幻冠带」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.42,0:21:05.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  突然就逃了可真不尽人情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.36,0:21:10.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的对手乃我是也
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.79,0:21:11.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开战
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.15,0:21:14.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微让我乐一乐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.47,0:21:23.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚拉斯托尔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.68,0:21:25.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你问过我想把悠二怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.66,0:21:27.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想让他怎么样的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.60,0:21:30.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那还没有想到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.41,0:21:31.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.02,0:21:32.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.53,0:21:35.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…喜欢悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.13,0:21:37.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在只想到这个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.56,0:21:38.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.67,0:21:40.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对…只有这个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.70,0:21:42.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有这个就能战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.10,0:21:44.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  你就叫夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.11,0:21:46.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从现在开始就这么叫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.37,0:21:49.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经不是单纯的火雾战士
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.13,0:21:52.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.62,0:21:54.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炎发灼眼的火雾战士？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.12,0:21:55.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.30,0:21:57.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我起的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.48,0:22:02.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时起  炎发灼眼的火雾战士就变成了夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.47,0:22:06.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.93,0:22:10.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊  因为是夏娜才会救我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.50,0:22:12.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为是夏娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.89,0:22:15.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对  因为不是普通的火雾战士
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.41,0:22:18.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样…我不就…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.01,0:22:26.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把她看成普通的火雾战士的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.01,0:22:28.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不就是我自己吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.33,0:22:44.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.91,0:22:45.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.81,0:22:47.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妨碍者
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.95,0:22:53.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二…绝对要救你！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.77,0:24:29.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灼眼的夏娜  最终话
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.29,0:24:32.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红莲的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.19,0:24:35.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时候
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.47,0:24:37.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少女在火焰中微笑
